\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid94243 {\f1\fs48\insrsid94243 \page }{\b\f1\fs56\ul\insrsid4196060\charrsid11601881 Introduction}{\b\f1\fs56\ul\insrsid4196060 
\par }{\f1\fs56\insrsid11601881\charrsid11601881 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid4196060 {\f2\fs28\insrsid4196060 
\par Since the late 1990\rquote }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 s,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4196060  there has been a dramatic increase in obesity in Americans}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 , regardless of}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4196060  age}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 ,}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid4196060  according to information collected and analyzed by the National Center for Health Statistics.
\par 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 Almost 9 million (15%)}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3546463  children between the ages of 6 and 19 are overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3546463  and this number is still growing }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 according to
}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3546463  information gathered between 199}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 9 and 2000 (triple the number of}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3546463  1980).  The information has also shown that another 15% of children }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 between }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid3546463 the ages of 6 and 19 are at risk of becoming overweight also.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4196060 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid3546463 
\par Obesity is defined as }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 having}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3546463  an excessive accumulation of body fat which will result in the }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 person\rquote s}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3546463  body}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678  being}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid3546463  about 20% heavier than their ideal body weight.  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090 So those people whose weight is above what is considered their ideal range}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090  are defined as being }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090 .  Obesity is a common eating disorder that is associated with teens.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3546463 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090 
\par Although teens may have fewer weight related health issues than adults, those teens }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 that}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090  are }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090  now are much more likely to be come }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090  as an adult.  Teens who are }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090 (in fact }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 people}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090  of all ages }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 that}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090  are }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090 ) are at risk from a number of different health issues}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 , and these include:}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090 

\par 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 1.\tab}}\pard \qj \fi-660\li1020\ri0\widctlpar\jclisttab\tx1020\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\ls12\adjustright\rin0\lin1020\itap0\pararsid11877090 {\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090 Heart Disease

\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 2.\tab}Diabetes
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 3.\tab}High Blood Pressure
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 4.\tab}Strokes
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 5.\tab}Some forms of Cancer
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid11877090 {\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090 
\par Those teens who are obese may find that they }{\f2\fs28\insrsid1006220 are not only physically unfit}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1006220 
 but their well being is usually very low as well.  Many obese people will also tend to have a shorter life expectancy than those who are the right weight for their body size.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid11877090 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 Plus}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074  it can also lead to social disabilities and unhappiness}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074  which in turn may cause them stress and in some cases}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074  may make them mentally ill as well.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1006220 
\par 
\par A study that was carried and details which were released in May 2004 suggested that overweight children are more likely to be involved in bullying than those children who are a normal weight.  But they can not only be the victims of bullying}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1006220  they may be the perpetrators as well.
\par 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid16146684 {\f2\fs28\insrsid16146684 The development of their own personal identity and body image is an important goal for any teenager.  
\par 
\par There are a number of causes fo}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 r obesity which center}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16146684  around an imbalance in the teens energy they put into their bodies}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16146684 
 (calories that they obtain from the food they eat) and the energy they release from their bodies (how good their metabolism is}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16146684  and how much physical activity they take part in).  Often teens }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 when a teen is}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16146684  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 , it is}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16146684  because there is a problem with the nutritional value of their diet, }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 or }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16146684 it may be psychological, familial or physiological}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 , all of}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16146684  which }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348 we will discu}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 
ss a little bit more}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348 .
\par 
\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348\charrsid6766565 The Family
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348 
\par Often children and teens are more at risk of becoming }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348  if they have two }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348  parents.  Although in some cases}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348  this may be due to a powerful genetic factor}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348  or it may be because they are modeling themselves }{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 after}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348  what they see their parents eating}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 . Also}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348  physical activities}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348  if any}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348 
 they take part in}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348  can indirectly affect the teen.  
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 
\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348\charrsid6766565 In Activity
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348 
\par On average}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348  an American child will spend several hours each day watching television}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15533603  or on a computer}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 . Compare this}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15533603 
 to years ago}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15533603  when this time would have been spent doing some form of physical activity instead.  There are }{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 a }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15533603 large amount of teens }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 and children}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15533603  who are now }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15533603  as they}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316  are}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15533603 
 expending little energy}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15533603  and often eat high calorie snacks whil}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 e }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15533603 watching TV or playing on the computer.  Today in the US}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,
}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15533603  about 1/3 of elementary school children carry out some form of physical education}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15533603  and less than 1/5 take part in physical activity programs after school.}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid12993348 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15533603 
\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid15533603\charrsid6766565 Heredity
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15533603 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid5315241 Recently}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid5315241  information has shown that heredity can influence fatness in a child and teen.  It was found that children born to }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid5315241  mothers have been found to be less active}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid5315241  and often gain more weight by the age of 3 months compared to those children born to mothers who are a normal weight}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid5315241  which suggests a possible inborn drive to conserve energy.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15533603 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid5315241 
\par In this book}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3762316 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid5315241  we will look at various ways in which help can be provided to }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid5315241  teens}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid5315241 
 and how they can lose weight successfully without them }{\f2\fs28\insrsid656047 res}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 orting}{\f2\fs28\insrsid656047  to fad diets etc.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid5315241 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid4196060 {\f2\fs28\insrsid4196060\charrsid4196060 
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid94243 {\f1\fs48\insrsid4196060 \page }{\b\f1\fs56\ul\insrsid5860976\charrsid11601881 Chapte}{\b\f1\fs56\ul\insrsid11601881\charrsid11601881 r 1 \endash  
\par }{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid11601881 
\par }{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid11601881\charrsid11601881 Psychological Issues for Teens Relating to Being Over}{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid5860976\charrsid11601881 weight}{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid4787394\charrsid11601881 
\par }{\b\f1\fs48\insrsid94243 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid94243 {\f2\fs28\insrsid94243 For many }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid94243  teens}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid94243 
 their physical health and well being are the least of their problems.  Much more relevant is the teasing and abuse they receive from t}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 heir peers at school and near}{\f2\fs28\insrsid94243  where they live.  }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 For many}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120  it is not only what others think of them that is upsetting}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120  but it }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 is what}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120  they actually think of themselves.  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid94243 A good percentage of teenagers (especially girls) are clinically depressed because they are so preoccupied with their weight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 . I}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid94243 t does not help that in every m}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 odel or every actress you see, and that people tend to}{\f2\fs28\insrsid94243  aspire to be}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid94243  are usually stick thin.
\par 
\par There is evidence now amounting to just how much pressure is being placed on obese teenagers}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 . A}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6045465  recent survey reveals that these kids rate the quality of life they have as low as that}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935  of young cancer patients while}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6045465  they are having chemotherapy.  There are other studies which have been carried out that report increased rates of depression, low se
lf esteem and isolation from other members of their age group}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6045465 
 which can result in behavioral problems in some.  These teenagers are less likely to be accepted into higher education (college) or to get married}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6045465  and }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 are }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid6045465 more likely to be part of the lower socioeconomic groups.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid94243 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6045465 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 What is worse is}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6045465  that many overweight teens will be hard on themselves}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6045465  and will often be mistreated by }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 others.}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid6045465   A study carried out in 2001 by Latner and Stunkard find}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 s}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6045465  that this }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 situation, rather}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6045465  than improving}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 
,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6045465  has steadily got worse.
\par 
\par Often}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6045465  those teen}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13977138 s who are overweight can suffer from other problems such as cardiovascular, }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 orthopedic}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13977138 
, gastrointestinal, respiratory, hormonal, neurological and metabolic diseases (diabetes).  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 These}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13977138  can often manifest themselves through psychological problems}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid13977138  and you may then have to ask for assistance from a trained professional in order to deal with them.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6045465 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid13977138 
\par Today in the US}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13977138  there are some weight loss programs for kids which are residential}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13977138  and combine psychological therapy with }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 behavior}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13977138  change therapy in order to improve the teens self esteem as well as their physical health.  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6045465 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid13977138 
\par So}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13977138  during this book}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13977138  we will look at ways in which those }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 teens,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13977138  who wish to lose weight}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13977138  can do so safely.  
\par 
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid13977138 {\insrsid13977138 \page }{\b\f1\fs56\ul\insrsid5860976\charrsid11601881 Chapter 2}{\b\f1\fs56\ul\insrsid13977138\charrsid11601881  }{
\b\f1\fs56\ul\insrsid16060222\charrsid11601881 \endash }{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid13977138\charrsid11601881  }{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid11601881 
\par 
\par Parenting Y}{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid11601881\charrsid11601881 our Overw}{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid16060222\charrsid11601881 eight Teen}{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid11601881\charrsid11601881  and Improving}{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid11601881  T}{
\b\f1\fs56\insrsid5860976\charrsid11601881 heir Self Esteem}{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid94243\charrsid11601881 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid16060222 {\f2\fs28\insrsid16060222 
\par 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid2063394 Today}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2063394  approximately 15% of children between the ages of 6 and 19 are either }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2063394 
 or obese (which is a 10% increase since 1970).  In fact}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2063394  there are now more than 9 million youngsters who are at risk from suffering some impaired life due to }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 high}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid2063394  blood pr}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 essure, high cholesterol levels or}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2063394  Type 2 Diabetes}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2063394  as well as having a negative self image of themselves}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2063394  which will continue as they grow into adulthood.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16060222 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid2063394 
\par There have been studies carried out that indicate }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9335612 a child who is obese at the age of 6}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9335612  will have a 50% chance of becoming obese as an adult.  Also}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid9335612  if one or both of the child\rquote s parents are }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9335612  then the chances increa
se to 80%.  These are very sobering and scary statistics for a parent whose child is }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9335612 .}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2063394 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9335612 
\par However}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9335612  there is good news that}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9335612  with help from the adults in their lives}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9335612 
 these children can be helped.  They can be taught healthier }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 behaviors}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9335612  which relate to both}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935  their eating habits and improving}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid9335612  the physical activit}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379 y they do}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379  and this will help them to lose the weight.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9335612 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 By helping them}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379  become more selective with the types of food that they consume}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 , and increasing}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379  the amount of physical activity that they }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 accomplish, it}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379  will only produce positive results.
\par 
\par However}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379  it should be stressed that formal dieting}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379  and especially giving you}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 r}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379 
 child a severely restricted diet}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379  should only be attempted with medical approval and the appropriate nutritional supervision.  Many pediatricians believe the best course is to try and hold an }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379  child\rquote s weight at a steady level}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 , and avoid}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379  losing large amounts of weight at a time}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379  until such a t}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9440935 ime as their height is at a}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379  healthier proportion to their weight.
\par 
\par The following 4 steps will not only help to facilitate healthier eating habits}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 but will}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379  also increase the amount of physical activity that they do.

\par 
\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid1262861\charrsid12587678 1.  Assessing }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 the}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid9982336  Health of Your Child and }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 whether}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid9982336  they are }{
\b\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678\charrsid11410678 overweight}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid1840379\charrsid12587678 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid1262861 Before you make any personal or environmental changes in your }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 teen\rquote s}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1262861  life}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1262861 
 take a few minutes to survey what your home life is like.  Do you allow them to lead a sedentary life}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1262861  and are they given plenty of chances to over eat at any time?  If you do}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1262861  then it is important that you bring any changes in to these areas of their life gradually.
\par 
\par First}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1262861  look at just how many hours your teen spends either watching TV}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1262861  or sitting at their computer.  A teen can}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 
 spend up to 24 hours a week}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1262861  watching TV}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6379986 .  Log any time that they spend doing either}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6379986  watching TV or on the computer}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid6379986  and try to reduce this by half.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1262861 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6379986 
\par When you have meals}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6379986  does your family gather around a table}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6379986  or do you eat most o}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 
f your meals sitting in front of the TV or computer?}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6379986   If you do, then try and make it a family rule that}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6379986  in }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 the }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6379986 future}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6379986 
 all food (including snacks) will be eaten in the kitchen or in the dining room at a table.  Such a small change has been shown to significantly reduce the amount of over eating that takes place in the home.
\par 
\par Next}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6379986  you will need to take a close look at you
r fridge and food cupboards.  Which foods do you have that you are most likely to eat when hunger hits you?  If the foods are high in fat, sweetened or low in nutritional value}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6379986 
 then why not try to find healthier alternatives instead}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6379986  suc}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 h as fresh fruit and vegetables?}{\f2\fs28\insrsid1262861 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6379986 
\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid6379986\charrsid12587678 2.  }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid9982336 Do Not Shame your Child into Losing Weight}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid6379986\charrsid12587678 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321 Neither adults }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 n}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321 or children can be shamed into losing weight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321  and an }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321  teen will know that they weigh too much.  But what a teen does not know}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321  is how they can achieve a normal weight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321 
 as well as increase their self esteem.  Teens like to know that their parents love them unconditionally, whether they are fat, thin or normal.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9335612 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321 
\par For any parent, mastering the fine art of loving our children just the way they are}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 , while}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321  helping them to achieve a healthier body}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987  can be difficult}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321 .  Any parent must learn to \'93give time\'94 and believe that the lessons we teach them will one day come to fruition.
\par 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid15560321 {\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321\charrsid15560321 This means that we can teach our youngsters to visualize that healthy plate (one which is half salad or vegetables
}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321\charrsid15560321  a quarter of starches and the remainder }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120\charrsid15560321 are}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321\charrsid15560321 
 made up of protein such as fish, meat, poultry or soy).  But you also know that at some point}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321\charrsid15560321  they will sneak either sweets or }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 cookie}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321\charrsid15560321 s into the home}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321\charrsid15560321  and upset the balance that you have achieved}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321 .}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2063394 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321 
\par A parent can persist in teaching their teens to see their plate before any food is put on it}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 .}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12942567  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 This}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12942567  is helpful}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid12942567  as it creates a sense of portion control that is helpful when the parent is not around to monitor what food the}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 y are actually having.  This}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12942567  porti
on control can also be practiced not just at home}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12942567  but when visiting a restaurant as well.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15560321 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12942567 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678 
\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid12942567\charrsid12587678 3.  Tak}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid9982336 e}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid12942567\charrsid12587678  up }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid9982336 some type of }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid12942567\charrsid12587678 Physical Activity as a Family
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12942567 The recommended amount of physical activity to be done by an adult is 30 minutes}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12942567  and 60 minutes for childr
en, which should be done several times a week.  However, if you are looking to lose weight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12942567  then more physical activity may be necessary.
\par 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid7153818 A great way of breaking the pattern of the }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 li}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ves}{\f2\fs28\insrsid7153818  that many }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 families}{\f2\fs28\insrsid7153818  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 
lead}{\f2\fs28\insrsid7153818  is to arrange activities that involve plenty of movement for the whole family together.  Not only do these types of activities burn calories}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid7153818 
 they can also serve as a setting for parent and child communication.  It is especially important in a child\rquote s teen years}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid7153818 
 when such opportunities for a parent to interact with their teen are at a premium.
\par 
\par Also}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid7153818  there is little or no financial cost involved in going for a walk or having a bike ride}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid7153818 
 and many communities now have either indoor or outdoor swimming pools which do not cost to much to use.  Just taking the family dog for a walk in the evening not only makes the dog happy}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid7153818 
 but will help to increase the family\rquote s metabolism.
\par 
\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid7153818\charrsid12587678 4. }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678\charrsid12587678 How to encourage the right sort of }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120\charrsid12587678 behavior}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid9982336  in your teen}{
\b\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678\charrsid12587678 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678 
\par The best way to help an }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678  or obese teen is through your own }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 behavior}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678 .  To}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 o}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678  often}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678  teens will do as an }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 adult}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678  does}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678  rather than what we tell them.
\par 
\par No parent can ask their child to turn off the TV when we are actually watching it in another room}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678  or
 to stop using the computer when they are spending hours themselves surfing the net.  Nor should they restrict the portions of food they eat}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678  when they}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678  themselves}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12587678  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid5995353 do not watch what they are eating.  Why would any child}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987  want to drink water or munch on}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid5995353  fruit or vegetables}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid5995353  when they see the adults around them drinking sugar laden soda or having a }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 bag}{\f2\fs28\insrsid5995353  of potato chips?
\par 
\par When looking to lead }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 a}{\f2\fs28\insrsid5995353  healthier kind of life style}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid5995353  it should be done one day at a time}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15360987 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid5995353 
 and the end result will be well worth the effort.
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid5995353 {\f2\fs28\insrsid5995353 \page }{\b\f1\fs56\ul\insrsid9982336\charrsid11601881 Chapter 3}{\b\f1\fs56\ul\insrsid11601881\charrsid11601881  \endash }{
\b\f1\fs56\insrsid11601881\charrsid11601881  
