\par Advice for Helping Teens}{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid5995353\charrsid11601881  Lose Weight}{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid7153818\charrsid11601881 
\par }{\f1\fs56\insrsid5995353 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid5995353 {\f2\fs28\insrsid216521 
Losing weight as a teen is far different from losing weight as an adult.  Weight loss in a teen depends on their age, the metabolic rate, their eating habits}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521  as well as the type of lifestyle the}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 y}{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521  lead.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid5995353 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521 
\par For many teens}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521  losing weight is easier than as an adult}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521  as the body burns calories much easier}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521 
 as well as quicker.  Often}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 , teens lead a much more active}{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521  lifestyle}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ;}{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521  they enjoy doing exercise, walking, 
jogging or participating in some form of sport.  These types of exercises will only help to boost a }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 teen\rquote s}{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521  metabolism}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521 
 and also increase the amount of calories that they burn.
\par 
\par Teens could start with one of the many fad diets that are around}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521  but they should only use these for about a week (anything longer will cause damage to their bodies).  After a week of using a fad diet}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521  they should then continue on a much more healthy diet regime}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521  and}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311  one}{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521  which allows them }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 to }{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521 lose weight more slowly (}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 which}{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521  is the best way to lose weight healthily).
\par 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9839173 When on a diet}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9839173  a teen should also lead a more active kind of }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 life;}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9839173  they can do this by exercising whenever possible}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9839173  or participate in some sporting activity.  This is especially important for teenagers}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9839173  as they are still growing}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 
, and they need more food while}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9839173  they are still growing.  So they need to exercise in order to help remove some of the extra calories they are gaining from the extra food they are eating.  So}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 
, get out and exercise. I}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9839173 f they sit around at home watching TV or playing on the computer}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9839173  they will soon find that their weight has increased.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid216521 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9839173 
\par As a teenager}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9839173  you have much more energy}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9839173  so why not put it to good use by taking up exercise or some sports activity.  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553 
It is best that a teen }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 that}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553  plays }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 a }{\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553 sport or do}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 es}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553  some physical activity}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 
,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553  should choose one that the}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 y enjoy and will have fun while}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553  doing it.  The best benefit is that they are not only exercising their }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 bodies}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553  but the will also be burning off the excess fat and calories}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553  and so improving their health.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9839173 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 It is imperative}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120  therefore}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 , for those teens to}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120  lead both an active life}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120  and have a healthy diet}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120  in order to achieve maximum performance and productivity.  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553 Many teens who lead such }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 li}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ves,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553  find that they are able to }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 do }{\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553 everything they want}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553  and d
o not suffer from fatigue or weakness when doing things.
\par 
\par 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid5995353 
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid4998553 {\insrsid4998553 \page }{\b\f1\fs56\ul\insrsid9982336\charrsid11601881 Chapter 4}{\b\f1\fs56\ul\insrsid4998553\charrsid11601881  \endash }{
