\par }{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid4998553\charrsid11601881 Some Simple Rules to Follow to Help Teens Lose Weight Safely}{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid5995353 
\par }{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid6827311\charrsid11601881 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid4998553 {\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553 
\par In this chapter}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553  we will look at some simple rules which should be followed as a parent if you wish to help you}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 r teen}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553  lose weight safely.
\par 
\par The key thing to a teen losing weight is that have much healthier habits}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12010902 .  Today}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12010902  teenage obesity is a growing problem}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12010902 
 and there is plenty you can do as a parent in order to help your teen with any weight problems they may have.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4998553 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12010902 
\par Although there is no magic formula to helping your teen lose weight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12010902  the real key to succeeding is by helping them to lead a healthier kind of life that they can }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 then }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid12010902 carry on into adulthood.
\par 
\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid12010902\charrsid4007541 1.  Talk to your Teen
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12010902 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 If your teen is }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120  then they are probably concerned about it too.  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12010902 
Aside from there being long term health issues involved}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12010902  such as high blood pressure or they may suffer from diabetes}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12010902 
 there are also the social and emotional issues involved as well.
\par 
\par Offer your teen the support and gentle understanding that they are looking for}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584  and help them to take control of the problem.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12010902 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584 
\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 
\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584\charrsid4007541 2.  Unrealistic Images
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid4007541 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584 For many teenage girls}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584  their weight and how they look can be a very delicate matter}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584 
 and you should remind them there is no perfect body out there.  Remind }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 them }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584 that}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584  what might the right weight for one person}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584  is not the right weight for somebody else.
\par 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid15341584 {\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584\charrsid15341584 Instead of talking to them about fat or thin}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584\charrsid15341584  encourage your teenage to focus on }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120\charrsid15341584 behaviors}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584\charrsid15341584  which will promote a much healthier weight.  If you want to}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584\charrsid15341584  talk to your family doctor}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584\charrsid15341584  and he will help to set realistic goals for you}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 r}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584\charrsid15341584  teenager with regard to body mass inde}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 x,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584\charrsid15341584  and the weight they should be based on their age, height and general health.}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584 
\par 
\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584\charrsid4007541 3.  }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid9982336 Resist Using Quick Fixes in order to lose weight rapidly}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584\charrsid4007541 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584 
\par Help you}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 r}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584  teenager }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 by teaching them}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584  how to lose weight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 , and then keep}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584 
 it off.  Many of the fad diets around are likely to rob your teen of essential nutrients, iron and calcium that they need in their diet}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584  as they are still growing.  
\par 
\par Don\rquote t allow them to take weight loss pills or other quick fixes}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584  as they will not address the root of the problem}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584 
 and the effects of these types of treatment are short lived.  
\par 
\par It is important to remember that only permanent changes in their habits will }{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895 help the weight they lose to stay away.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15341584 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895 
\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895\charrsid4007541 4.  }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid9982336 Increase the amount of physical activity your teen does}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895\charrsid4007541 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895 
\par Like any adult}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 a}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895  teenager will need to do about 60 minutes of physical activ
ity each day.  But this does not mean that they have to do it all at once.  They can}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895  instead}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895 
 do the activity in short bursts throughout the day in order to help burn off any excess calories or fat.
\par 
\par Team sports}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895  which they do at school or at a local sports hall}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 , are}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895  a great way for your teen to get active.  However, if your child isn\rquote 
t an athlete}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895  or finds it difficult to participate in certain sports}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895  then encourage them to walk, cycle or skate to and from school}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895  or just to walk a few times }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 a}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895 
round the school before they begin classes.  Why not suggest that they spend at least one of each day away from the computer and do something a little more physical (may be you can get t}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 hem to take the dog for a walk)?}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895   
\par 
\par Try and get them to do some household chores}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895  like vacuuming or washing the car}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6827311 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895  as they have aerobic benefits as well.
\par 
\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895\charrsid4007541 5.  Ensure }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid467760 that your teen}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895\charrsid4007541  ha}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid467760 s}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895\charrsid4007541  Breakfast
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895 
\par If you have a teenager who find}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 s that it\rquote s}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895  to}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 o}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895  difficult to get}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806  up,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895 
 try to get them up a little earlier than normal in order }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 for them to}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895  have some breakfast.  How many times have you heard people say \'93breakfast is the most important meal of the day\'94}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 ?}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895   A good nutritious breakfast will help jump start their day }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 AND}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895  their metabolism}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895 
 and will provide them with the energy they need to face the day ahead.  You may also find that it stops them from eating too much during the rest of the day as well.
\par 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 If your teen is not keen on high fiber cereal or whole wheat toast}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120  then why not suggest they eat what was left over from the night before.  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid4007541 
You could even suggest a piece of cheese, a small handful of nuts and a piece of fruit instead}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4007541  as they will be just as good for them}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4007541 
 and do the same job as the cereal or toast does.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2975895 
