\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid3821150\charrsid3821150 6.  }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid467760 If your teen snacks}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 ,}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid467760  teach them to snack wisely}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid3821150\charrsid3821150 
