\par When it comes to the portions that a teen eats, size really does matter.  If you can}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3821150  encourage your child to cut back and to stop eating when they feel full.  You may find that just one slice of pizza}
{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3821150  or half the pasta on the plate is enough to make them feel full. }{\f2\fs28\insrsid8872375 
