ou find in fruit juice, special}{\f2\fs28\insrsid8872375 ty coffees and }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 other drinks can also add up }{\f2\fs28\insrsid8872375 quickly as well.  So getting your teenager to drink more water}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 ,}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid8872375  instead of soda and other sugary drinks}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid8872375  will save on the }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 calories}{\f2\fs28\insrsid8872375  and their sugar intake as well.  Why not suggest t
hat they drink }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 flavored}{\f2\fs28\insrsid8872375  water, seltzer wate}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 r or unsalted club soda instead?}{\f2\fs28\insrsid8872375 
