\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 \'85}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3541206 or that they share a snack with their friend}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3541206  instead of having an order to themselves.  
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 
