\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid3541206\charrsid3611596 11.  Be Positive in your Attitude}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid467760  when helping your teen to lose weight}{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid3541206\charrsid3611596 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid3541206 
\par Being }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3541206  does not always lead to a lifetime of low self esteem, but your acceptance of your }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 teen\rquote s}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3541206 
 weight problem is critical.  Remember to listen to your }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 teen\rquote s}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3541206  concerns regarding their weight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3541206 
 and comment on their skills, efforts and accomplishments.
\par 
\par Make it perfectly clear to your child that your love for them is unconditional}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3541206  and not dependent on how they look.  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid13657904 Why not help your teen learn 
to express their feelings in much healthier ways}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13657904  say by writing d}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 own what they feel in a journal?}{\f2\fs28\insrsid3541206 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid13657904 
\par If you}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 r}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13657904  child is struggling with low self esteem}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13657904  and finding it difficult to cope with their weight in a healthy way}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 ,}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid13657904  then consider looking for a support group, formal weight control program or professional counseling to help them. 
\par 
\par There are many support groups around which will provide your teen with the tools to counter any social pressure and cultivate a positive attitude with regard to their self esteem}{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 .}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13657904  }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 T}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13657904 his will help them to }{\f2\fs28\insrsid12935806 take control of their weight. }{\f2\fs28\insrsid13657904 These benefits will then last them a life time.
\par 
