\par }{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid11601881\charrsid11601881 Weight Loss for Teens \endash  A Parent Should Not W}{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid16388120\charrsid11601881 orry}{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid11601881\charrsid11601881  Too M}{\b\f1\fs56\insrsid3611596\charrsid11601881 uch}{
\b\f1\fs56\insrsid12465690\charrsid11601881 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid16388120 {\f2\fs28\insrsid16388120 
\par Concerns are always }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 being}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16388120  raised in relation to the dangers of child or teen weigh loss}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15952251 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16388120  especially with }{\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229 parents}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid16388120 .
\par 
\par For many teens today}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15952251 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16388120  the image of the body is at the fore front of their minds}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15952251 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16388120  especially when you look at the models used in magazines etc.

\par 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229 Teenagers will be easily swayed by their peers or TV/Movie idols}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15952251 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229  and some will go to drastic measures in order to look as good}{\f2\fs28\insrsid15952251 ,}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229  and wear the clothes that their heroes are wearing.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16388120 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229 
\par More and more teenagers are suffering from either anorexia }{\f2\fs28\insrsid15952251 or}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229  bulimia (both very serious illnesses)}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 both of}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229  which they can ofte}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 n easily hide from their parents}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229 .
\par 
\par It is very difficult to understand how anorexia and bulimia affects people who}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229  to others}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229  may look healthy and }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 being a}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229  normal size weight.  For many sufferers}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229  they see themselves as fat and undesirable}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229 
 and they usually lack self confidence and self esteem.  They may feel this because they have been laughed at when they were younger}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229  or it can be that they are just to}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 o}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229  shy or embarrassed to discuss how they feel.
\par 
\par But whatever the reason}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229  those suffering from either anorexia or bulimia are at risk.  Their health will become compromised (not now but may be later on in life).  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047 
Should such eating problems not be diagnosed earl}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 y}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047  enough}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047  then the damage they cause to their body may be irreversible.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4603229 

\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047 
\par You can not force a person to eat if they don\rquote t want to}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047 
 and neither can you stop a person from purging themselves.  What you need to do is get to the root of their problem and discuss with them how they feel about themselves}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 .}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 F}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047 ind out why they feel that they need to lose the weight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877  in such a manner}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047 .  Then you can look at ways in which you can help them to combat this problem.  
\par 
\par However}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047  those people who are suffering either from anorexia or }{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 bulimia}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047  will most likely need professional help (you don\rquote t 
need to send them a way to rehab)}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 . T}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047 here are plenty of self help groups which have now been set up to }{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 aid}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047  with these eating }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 disorders}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047 .  
\par 
\par How do I recognize if my teen is suffering from an eating }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 problem?}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047   Unfortunately}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047  most people}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047 
 especially children}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047  are good at hiding the symptoms related to eating problems.  But below are some }{\f2\fs28\insrsid13650439 signs that should help.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4089047 
