 or say they are not hungry or that they earlier when they were out with their friends.  Others may well skip breakfast and just grab something on the way school}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13650439  or they won\rquote 
t take the lunch that you have prepared for them to school}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 \'85}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13650439 or if they do}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13650439 
 they throw away as soon as you are out of sight.  Discreetly check with the school to see if they are eating meals at school}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13650439  and if you are able to}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid13650439  speak to their friends and find out what}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13650439  if anything}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13650439 
 they are eating when they are with them.  However, it is important that you do not pry too much}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13650439  or it will lead to them only hiding the problem from you even more.
\par 
\par If you are able to}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13650439  monitor what they are reading and logging onto on the internet.
\par 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 For many teens}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120  they will deny that they have a problem where eating is concerned.  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16519754 
Parents must find a way to get past the idea that there is nothing troubling the teen}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16519754  and that they go through stages when they don\rquote 
t like certain foods or they will avoid eating a meal with the family.  However, if you are reading this chapter and you see things in it which seem familiar in relation to your teen}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16519754 
 then it may be worth taking a further look at your teen\rquote s lifestyle.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13650439 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16519754 
\par Today}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16519754  there is a lot of pressure being put on teens to become vegetarians}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16519754 
 and some vegetarians will allow fish as part of their diets.  This is okay as this provides the necessary nutrients, Vitamin B12, zinc and }{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 iron, which}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16519754  a teen wil}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 l need while
}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16519754  they are growing.  However, it is wise to show them which fish are the best to eat more often}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16519754  and which they should eat less of.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid13650439 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16519754 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 It is the}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16519754  teens wh}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 o}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16519754  give up meat and fish altogether that a parent should be concerned about.  Protein is 
important for us to grow, maintain healthy muscles, skin, hair and good health.  The best source for protein is from animals}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16519754 
 and those teens who give up this source will need to get it from other areas}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16519754  such as through vitamin supplements.  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 S}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288 
tudies carried out claim that the quantity of nutrition provided by pills is not the same}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288  or as good as they would get from animal sources.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid16519754 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288 
\par Therefore}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288  as a parent}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288  if you should have any concerns in regard to what is written above}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288 
 it is time to take action.
\par 
\par A great way of doing this is to help your teen to understand why they should eat properly}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288  and what foods they should be eating}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288 
 as well as how much and when and what they should avoid.  Not only will this help you}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288  but it will help your teen}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877  to}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 bett
er }{\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288 understand the importance of food}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288  and what we need to have a healthy body}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288  a}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 s well as}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288  the best ways to combat weight gain naturally.
\par 
\par So now is the right time }{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 for}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288  you}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877  to}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288  take action with regard to your }{\f2\fs28\insrsid16136120 teen\rquote s}{\f2\fs28\insrsid4152288 
 health and any concerns they may have about their body image and weight.
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 
