\par As you can see from this book}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid656047  there are number of ways in which helping a teen to cope with their obesity}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 , as well as}{\f2\fs28\insrsid656047  help}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 
ing}{\f2\fs28\insrsid656047  them lose weight safely.
\par 
\par Often}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10447877 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid656047  obesity treatment programs which have been devised for }{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 teens}{\f2\fs28\insrsid656047 
 rarely have weight loss as a goal, but rather they aim to slow or halt any weight gain so that the teen will grow into their body weight over the next few months or years.  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6766565 It is estimated that for every 20% excess 
of body weight a teen has}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6766565  they will need about 1\'bd years weight maintenance to obtain their ideal body weight.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid656047 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6766565 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 So,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6766565  early and appropriate intervention on the part of the parent is particularly valuable.  It has been found that modifying a teens eating and exercise habits is much easier to do than with an adult.  

\par 
\par The three forms of intervention that a parent coul}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 d use are as follows:}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6766565 
\par 
\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid6766565\charrsid6766565 Physical Activity
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6766565 
\par By adopting a formal exercise program}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6766565  or just simply becoming more active}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid6766565  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 you }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6766565 
will help to burn fact and increase the amount of energy a teen expends.  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 Studies have shown that exercise}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074  as well as coupling it with one of the other forms of intervention}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074  is a successful way to help them lose weight}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834  safely}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 .  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid6766565 
\par 
\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid10636061 Diet
\par 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid10636061 It is advisable that you do n}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ot allow your teen to fast or drastically reduce}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10636061  their calorie intake.  Not only }{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 is this way of losing weight}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid10636061  psychologically stressful on them}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10636061  but it may adversely affect their growth}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10636061  and what a teen sees as \'93normal eating\'94
.  So making sure that they have a balanced diet}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10636061  with moderate restrictions on the amount of calories they have}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10636061  is ideal.  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid22763 
A great way is to reduce dietary fat}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 , which}{\f2\fs28\insrsid22763  has been found as a successful way of treating teens }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 that}{\f2\fs28\insrsid22763  are }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid22763 .  }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 It may be that you}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 r}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074  teen needs to be educated on the nutritional values of foods}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074  also.  }{
\f2\fs28\insrsid22763 So by controlling a }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 teen\rquote s}{\f2\fs28\insrsid22763  diet}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid22763  and getting them to do more exercise}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid22763 
 will help to treat their weight problem.}{\f2\fs28\insrsid10636061 
\par }{\f2\fs28\insrsid22763 
\par }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid22763 Modification of a Teens }{\b\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 Behavior}{\f2\fs28\insrsid22763 
\par 
\par There are many }{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 behavioral}{\f2\fs28\insrsid22763  strategies that are used on adults}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid22763  which can be success}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 fully applied to teens, such as:}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid22763 
\par 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f2\fs28\insrsid22763 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 1.\tab}}\pard \qj \fi-840\li1200\ri0\widctlpar\jclisttab\tx1200\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\ls14\adjustright\rin0\lin1200\itap0\pararsid22763 {\f2\fs28\insrsid22763 
Self monitoring and recording the food they have
