\par This book has hopefully helped with ways in which you can help your teen with any weight issues they may have.  However}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074  it is easier to prevent a teen from being }{\f2\fs28\insrsid11410678 overweight}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074  than it is to treat it.  
\par 
\par Where prevention is concerned}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074  it focuses on educating the parents about providing their children with a good nutritional diet and plenty of physical activity.  However}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{
\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074  where such preventive measures can not help those teens who suffer from weight problems because of a heredity factor}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074 
 then the education of the parents should be focused on building up their teens self esteem}{\f2\fs28\insrsid2162834 ,}{\f2\fs28\insrsid9450074  and addressing any psychological issues that they may have.
\par 
